I"!<ol>
  <li>
    <p>vscode中先安装 <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=sneezry.watch-in-chrome">Watch in Chrome</a>插件</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>再安装chrome插件 <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/vs-code-watch-in-chrome/mmbnmofkiadlcapnmgnkheoadkpeefii">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/vs-code-watch-in-chrome/mmbnmofkiadlcapnmgnkheoadkpeefii</a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>vscode打开命令框,输入watch in chrome就可以打开chrome(设置为默认浏览器)</p>
  </li>
</ol>
